data.description: Space, Space and More Space!! This big four bedroom, three bath home dotes two suites! Each with full bathroom and walk in closet. With a formal living room, family room AND den the possibilities for an in home office, play room or man cave are endless! The massive detached, two story, two car garage  in the rear of the home has plenty of room for all of your storage needs! The additional storage building would make the most adorable crafting space! With open front porch, long screened in back porch AND deck, all of your outdoor coffee sipping, bird watching, porch rocking chair needs are sure to be met! Located in Hope Mills with a simple commute to Ft. Liberty, shopping dining and the Hope Mills Park. Seller is offering $5k towards buyer closing costs and installing NEW LVP flooring in the living room and hallway! Call your favorite agent for a tour today!
